| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4960 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e6b7ac9-dd59-5872-a0ee-e5ec320acd69"
